cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.SD 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with natural language processing tasks such as intent classification. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes a novel multi-layer ensembling approach to improve performance on intent classification. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with developing models for language understanding tasks. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is a possible category as intent classification is a sub-task of information retrieval. 
- cs.SD (Software Engineering) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper may discuss software engineering aspects of developing and implementing the proposed approach.
